parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents.

the engine oil pressure warning light illuminates

the vehicle loses power and acceleration
and the timing chain guide breaks apart.

the engine stalls or shuts off

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the timing chain can cause the engine to seize or stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The drivetrain malfunction warning light illuminates
the engine stalls or seizes
the vehicle loses power
the timing chain noise is audible
the engine oil is contaminated with metal shavings
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear.
